---
title: Spiced Chickpea and Spinach Stew with Bocconcini and Garlic Naan
description: This spiced chickpea stew is inspired by shakshuka – a Middle-Eastern dish featuring eggs cooked in a simmered, savoury tomato sauce. We've given our version a HelloFresh twist by swapping out eggs for creamy bocconcini cheese!
